caption:
In the 2011 Champions League semifinal between FC Barcelona and Real Madrid, a pitch invader named Jimmy Jump ran onto the field wearing a shirt that read “Qatar 2022”.. 🇶🇦👀

At the time, Qatar had only recently won the bid to host the 2022 FIFA World Cup in December 2010.

In the background stood none other than Lionel Andrés messi, unaware of what he was witnessing. Little did he know that over a decade later, in that very country, he would achieve the greatest dream of his career: becoming a World Champion.

And he did it in Qatar. 🇦🇷🏆

Destiny! 🩵
